com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.message.resthttp

Class PayLoadMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.message.Message
      • com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.message.OutMessage
        • com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.message.resthttp.PayLoadMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PostMessage, PutMessage

    public abstract class PayLoadMessage
extends OutMessage
    An abstract representation of the OutMessage that will be sent to the server with payload data in the request. The payload data is the Serializable message body that is converted to JSON format and sent to the server
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Neebal Technologies
    See Also:
    PostMessage, PutMessage, Serialized Form
